It's happening! This project has been in the works since before COVID.
I'm collaborating with @humblematerials to bring you the most unhinged, off the wall adaptation of The Yellow Wallpaper, in a way that's NEVER been done! Prepare to lose your mind 🫨, the women in the wall can't wait to meet you. Ticket link in my bio. 4 shows only! If you're in or near Philly don't miss this!
